>> name: Mayonnaise

Add @egg to food processor and process for 20 seconds

Add @mustard{1%tbsp}, @vinegar{1%tbsp} and @salt{1/4%tsp}, process for 20 seconds

Scrape down sides

Add the neutral (non-EVOO) @oil{1%cup} very slowly until about 1/4 is added

Continue to add a little less slowly until all oil is added

Season with @lemon{1%tsp}, extra vinegar and salt as needed
